201
00:17:23,417 --> 00:17:27,421
He tried to assassinate the president.
It was an act of insurrection.

202
00:17:28,047 --> 00:17:28,881
Sang-un.

203
00:17:29,381 --> 00:17:31,216
We need to expose the truth.

204
00:17:35,387 --> 00:17:36,847
Only if you are prepared

205
00:17:37,890 --> 00:17:39,725
