208
00:17:57,034 --> 00:17:58,160
Should I come over, sir?

209
00:17:59,578 --> 00:18:01,121
Or will you bring your ass here?

210
00:18:03,999 --> 00:18:06,919
SAFE HOUSE IN SAMCHEONGDONG

211
