since the Cabinet meeting a month ago.

218
00:18:41,954 --> 00:18:44,540
-Rejecting a routine report--
-You should go.

219
00:18:44,623 --> 00:18:46,792
Park Dong-ho will show up soon.

220
00:18:54,466 --> 00:18:57,928
Prime Minister Park
will be arrested tomorrow morning.

221
