since he is bound to go to prison.

225
00:19:10,023 --> 00:19:12,359
Half the people I meet are scumbags.

226
00:19:12,442 --> 00:19:15,112
The rest are untrustworthy.
So I developed this habit.

227
00:19:16,655 --> 00:19:19,283
I'm sure you wiped the CCTV footage
and access records,

228
00:19:20,951 --> 00:19:21,827
but not this.

229
00:19:34,298 --> 00:19:35,716
Well,

230
00:19:35,799 --> 00:19:37,885
I planted a tree in the Blue House.

231
00:19:38,385 --> 00:19:41,138
Some bastard chopped it down
before it could bear fruit.

232
00:19:42,806 --> 00:19:45,934
So I would like you to be my tree
in the Blue House.

233
00:19:47,936 --> 00:19:49,897
Just give me half of the fruit,

234
00:19:50,939 --> 00:19:52,733
and you eat the other half.

235
00:19:53,609 --> 00:19:54,484
